WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.170
You don't have a traffic problem. You have a positioning problem.

00:00:04.170 --> 00:00:12.910
Markets reward the obvious choice. Positioning is the space you occupy in someone's mind, relative to every alternative they could pick instead.

00:00:12.910 --> 00:00:19.130
When that space is unclear, more traffic just means more people confirming they don't know what you do.

00:00:19.130 --> 00:00:28.630
Before spending another dollar on ads, ask one question. If a stranger saw your page for three seconds, could they say what you do and why it's different?

00:00:28.630 --> 00:00:32.330
More traffic multiplies the confusion. Clarity fixes it.

00:00:32.330 --> 00:00:36.170
Clarity earns attention. Confusion just rents it.

00:00:36.170 --> 00:00:39.500
Perception and attention intelligence.

00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:46.330
If you want a clear read on where you stand, the audit is free. No pitch. Just arstrategies.com.
